What is Devops?

In the fast-paced world of software development, where agility and efficiency are paramount, the term "DevOps" has emerged as a crucial concept. Yet, for many, it remains shrouded in mystery. What exactly is DevOps, and why
has it become such a vital part of modern software engineering? Let's delve into the world of DevOps and uncover its significance.

